a(S'Central processing unit (CPU)'
p24381
g19085
tp24382
a(S'The control unit, ALU, and registers are collectively known as a central processing unit (CPU). Early CPUs were composed of many separate components but since the mid 1970s CPUs have typically been constructed on a single integrated circuit called a microprocessor.'
p24383
